Did you know that Dust and allergens are widely spread on various surfaces of your home including sofas and beds, and may not even be visible to the naked eye? 

I was shocked to know when I attended Dyson’s event on their Global Dust Study that you might find the most skin flakes probably not on your floors, but rather beds, sofas, pet beds – the places we spend the most time but clean the least. In fact, beds can contain between 100,000 and more than 1 million dust mites.

So, what can you do about it?
Eliminate dust completely by vacuuming your home regularly, not only the floors but all the surfaces. And, that’s why I use my Dyson vacuum cleaner with its versatile attachments that helps me keep my home clean and healthy.
